<p>On May 1st, 2023, I’ll officially start as an Assistant Professor and PI of the <a href="https://pivlab.org/">Pividori Lab</a> in the <a href="https://medschool.cuanschutz.edu/dbmi">Department of Biomedical Informatics</a>, <a href="https://medschool.cuanschutz.edu/">University of Colorado Anschutz Medical Campus</a>.
I won’t write a long post about this, just saying that I’m very excited about this new stage in my career.
I invite you to keep an eye on this blog, <a href="https://twitter.com/miltondp">my Twitter</a> and <a href="https://github.com/pivlab">our projects on GitHub</a> for updates about our research and other activities.</p>

<p><strong>We are recruiting!</strong> So if your interests overlap with <a href="https://pivlab.org/research/">our labs’</a>, please reach out!</p>

